      <title>中国抗议台湾部长在美国支持的首尔峰会上扮演的角色</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-protests-taiwan-ministers-role-seoul-summit-backed-by-us-2024-03-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国周一斥责韩国台湾参加美国支持的首尔民主峰会，台湾数字部长唐奥黛在峰会上发表了未经宣布的视频致辞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-protests-taiwan-ministers-role-seoul-summit-backed-by-us-2024-03-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 11:09:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦央行维持利率在22%不变</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/pakistans-central-bank-keeps-interest-rate-hold-22-2024-03-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于通胀风险持续隐现，巴基斯坦央行周一连续第六次召开政策会议，将关键利率维持在 22%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/pakistans-central-bank-keeps-interest-rate-hold-22-2024-03-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 10:55:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国他信展现权力，效忠者趋之若鹜</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailands-thaksin-projects-power-loyalists-cosy-up-2024-03-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[政界人士蜂拥而至，与泰国总理共进晚餐，还有警察护送他去往的地方，亿万富翁、前总理他信·西那瓦这个周末看起来更像是一位政治家，而不是一名被假释的罪犯。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailands-thaksin-projects-power-loyalists-cosy-up-2024-03-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 10:42:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚前总理马哈蒂尔感染后出院</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/malaysias-former-pm-mahathir-discharged-hospital-after-infection-2024-03-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚前总理马哈蒂尔·穆罕默德办公室周一表示，他因感染入院近三个月后于周一出院。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/malaysias-former-pm-mahathir-discharged-hospital-after-infection-2024-03-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 07:29:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>塔利班称在阿富汗空袭造成8人死亡后对巴基斯坦军方进行了反击</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistan-carried-out-two-air-strikes-inside-afghanistan-killed-8-people-taliban-2024-03-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿富汗塔利班周一表示，巴基斯坦对其领土进行了两次空袭，造成五名妇女和三名儿童死亡，其安全部队向巴基斯坦军方发射重型武器进行报复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistan-carried-out-two-air-strikes-inside-afghanistan-killed-8-people-taliban-2024-03-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 07:06:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>2023年更多中国人结婚，结婚率九年来首次上升</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/more-chinese-tied-knot-2023-lifting-marriage-rates-first-time-nine-years-2024-03-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2023年，中国的新婚人数较上年增长了12.4%，扭转了近十年来的下降趋势，因为越来越多的年轻人因COVID-19大流行而推迟了婚礼。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/more-chinese-tied-knot-2023-lifting-marriage-rates-first-time-nine-years-2024-03-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 07:04:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>解释者：韩国为何主办“民主峰会”？</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/why-is-south-korea-hosting-summit-democracy-2024-03-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈本周与美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯和其他外国官员一起呼吁在首尔主办民主峰会期间采取措施应对数字对自由的威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/why-is-south-korea-hosting-summit-democracy-2024-03-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 06:01:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国警告新加坡公民远离赌博</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-warns-citizens-singapore-stay-away-gambling-2024-03-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国驻新加坡大使馆周一敦促新加坡公民远离一切形式的赌博，称海外赌博违反中国法律。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-warns-citizens-singapore-stay-away-gambling-2024-03-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 04:45:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>电动汽车制造商 VinFast 创始人发起全球充电站合资企业</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/founder-ev-maker-vinfast-launches-global-charging-stations-firm-2024-03-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南电动汽车制造商 VinFast 的创始人周一成立了一家电动汽车充电站公司 V-Green，他表示该公司将优先在全球范围内支持 VinFast 汽车。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/founder-ev-maker-vinfast-launches-global-charging-stations-firm-2024-03-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 04:21:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于通胀担忧，台湾将维持利率稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/taiwan-set-hold-rates-steady-amid-inflation-concerns-2024-03-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[路透调查中的经济学家表示，预计台湾央行本周将维持政策利率稳定，并维持到明年初，以应对持续存在的通胀担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/taiwan-set-hold-rates-steady-amid-inflation-concerns-2024-03-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 04:14:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
